column1: Please do not change the template headings.
First data column must be blank.
If you are uploading new records, leave the "name" (ID) column blank.
If you are uploading new records, "Naming Series" becomes mandatory, if present.
Only mandatory fields are necessary for new records. You can delete non-mandatory columns if you wish.
For updating, you can update only selective columns.
You can only upload upto 5000 records in one go. (may be less in some cases)

column12: Thanks for your interest! Please take a few moments to fill this form. The better you tell us who you are, the better chances are that we want to have you in our team.
column13: Thanks for applying. If we find your profile interesting, we will get back to you. In the mean-time you can always edit your application.
column26: Not what your friends call you
An email id you check frequently
Want to share a resume? Link to a document via Dropbox or other similar file sharing tools
Already on GitHub / Bitbucket / Dribbble? Do you blog? Yay! Share your profile.
Tell us about your interests, your influences, what do you do in your free time.

column19: What have you done till now?
column26: Your past is the best pointer to your future. Share your achievements, like what is the toughest thing you have done? What is your superpower? Any pet projects?
Yes we know everyone needs a job, but why us? Go through our website and find what interests you. Why do you think working with us is the best decision you will ever make.
